    "step 5": {
        "implementation details": "III. Analysis of expression levels, coding potential, length, and exon count of transcripts:\n\u2460 Expression Levels:\n(1) Average expression values in FPKM (Fragments Per Kilobase of transcript per Million mapped reads) were calculated for protein-coding genes, known annotated lncRNA transcripts, and novel unannotated lncRNAs in liposarcoma cell lines.",
        "original text": "III. Analysis of expression levels, coding potential, length, and exon count of transcripts:\n\u2460 Expression Levels:\nThe novel unannotated lncRNA transcripts showed low expression and were comparable to known annotated lncRNAs in contrast to higher expression of protein-coding genes (Fig. 1A).",
