        "original text": "III. Analysis of expression levels, coding potential, length, and exon count of transcripts:\n\u2461 Coding Potential:\nAlso, these novel lncRNAs revealed lower coding potential scores and shorter length density compared to protein-coding genes but are consistent with the known annotated lncRNAs (Fig. 1B and C).",
        "results": "The coding potential of the novel unannotated lncRNAs was found to be lower compared to protein-coding genes, consistent with known annotated lncRNAs.",
        "results original text": "Also, these novel lncRNAs revealed lower coding potential scores and shorter length density compared to protein-coding genes but are consistent with the known annotated lncRNAs (Fig. 1B and C)."
