        "original text": "For further in vitro validation of FOXM1 in liposarcoma, FOXM1 was silenced using shRNA and achieved about 84\u201395% reduction in protein levels using two different shRNAs (sh2 and sh3) compared to Nt shRNA in LPS141 and LP6 cells (Fig. 6B).",
        "results": "Silencing of FOXM1 using shRNA2 and shRNA3 resulted in an 84-95% reduction in FOXM1 protein levels in LPS141 and LP6 cells.",
